da9f82ec-8672-42de-92ad-aa39a4e892ce.title: Alice
da9f82ec-8672-42de-92ad-aa39a4e892ce.text: Hello. How can I help you?

options.text: Can you give me any Farming advice?

b84ea109-11cc-461a-b24b-60e2ff6c141f.title: Alice
b84ea109-11cc-461a-b24b-60e2ff6c141f.text: Hello. How can I help you?

options.text: Can you give me any Farming advice?

d120a286-28a3-40e8-9f89-7399a0b7d898.title: <player>
d120a286-28a3-40e8-9f89-7399a0b7d898.text: Can you give me any Farming advice?

9acfe02e-8d96-4ebc-ae13-c3195d150e5a.title: Alice
9acfe02e-8d96-4ebc-ae13-c3195d150e5a.text:
Hello, friend, and thanks for allowing me to talk to my
husband. How can I help you?

ed14fdbf-f7ff-4710-b4aa-e709dba880e9.title: <player>
ed14fdbf-f7ff-4710-b4aa-e709dba880e9.text:
I am after one of your, er, unhealthier poultry. Could
you help me?

40ba7768-b958-47de-80aa-cd293a50b309.title: Alice
40ba7768-b958-47de-80aa-cd293a50b309.text:
You need those useless, undead chickens? How odd you
adventurers are.

2cb7b930-5341-4282-880c-fd67c8e3b288.title: Alice
2cb7b930-5341-4282-880c-fd67c8e3b288.text:
You need to talk to my husband though - not that I
can these days.

c73d160b-ec7a-4836-b2bd-c7fd2fb25914.title: Alice
c73d160b-ec7a-4836-b2bd-c7fd2fb25914.text: Can't you see, he is dead. I can't talk to the dead.

f406d6b7-cd54-4e5b-b2a4-cd1dde645c23.title: <player>
f406d6b7-cd54-4e5b-b2a4-cd1dde645c23.text:
I have a message from your husband. He wants you to
know that he still loves you, despite his ghostly state.

f7e2e7f7-4ea9-4a7d-bafc-0a87b6406c1c.title: Alice
f7e2e7f7-4ea9-4a7d-bafc-0a87b6406c1c.text:
The curse of undeath was so cruel; all the men out
here succumbed, but Lyra and I were left alive.

52d53941-e78e-4314-a9b6-e842e0c1a281.title: Alice
52d53941-e78e-4314-a9b6-e842e0c1a281.text: Ever since that day, I've not been able to speak to him.

68f630a2-1536-4ca3-83c6-110d220ddbf9.title: Alice
68f630a2-1536-4ca3-83c6-110d220ddbf9.text:
Tell him I love him but I can't find our savings. I
know he had our collection of gold and 'prize cow'
rosettes just before the curse struck.

bcfa6c8c-8aa1-4498-9b64-9974eafe84a5.title: <player>
bcfa6c8c-8aa1-4498-9b64-9974eafe84a5.text:
I'll have a word with him, then; magic has its uses I
suppose.

ae77cfc7-ce7d-4d2e-b9a8-db90472a3bf2.title: Alice
ae77cfc7-ce7d-4d2e-b9a8-db90472a3bf2.text: Have you spoken to my husband yet?

49a73f94-200a-49f7-a01d-0ad9bfd086d3.title: Alice
49a73f94-200a-49f7-a01d-0ad9bfd086d3.text: I'll need his bank pass, in that case.

5ac8b0c5-0ab3-4f00-85e8-f94290f1b24c.title: <player>
5ac8b0c5-0ab3-4f00-85e8-f94290f1b24c.text: Your husband says he put the cash in the bank.

f0bb5583-955c-45dd-b2cd-f10f75ccd2cc.title: <player>
f0bb5583-955c-45dd-b2cd-f10f75ccd2cc.text:
Can't you just take a ghostspeak amulet? Then you
could talk to him directly.

b44c40cd-d83d-47d0-bc4a-e13f81752f37.title: Alice
b44c40cd-d83d-47d0-bc4a-e13f81752f37.text:
I tried that once, but all those other ghosts - and even
the undead chickens and cows - scared me so much. I
wouldn't try it again for all the cash in Varrock bank.

54a4d001-9749-485a-a65b-bc9ce8b4ddaf.title: Alice
54a4d001-9749-485a-a65b-bc9ce8b4ddaf.text: Have you asked him about the bank pass?

850acfde-eb0b-4a2a-abba-da36462b7c53.title: <player>
850acfde-eb0b-4a2a-abba-da36462b7c53.text: He says he won't trust me with the bank pass.

52b63379-976c-4f9b-ac50-ac0d6a91738a.title: <player>
52b63379-976c-4f9b-ac50-ac0d6a91738a.text:
What if I gave some sort of altered ghostspeak amulet
to him - surely that would work?

0308ec53-d0b3-4fbf-bd2f-404a685f5472.title: Alice
0308ec53-d0b3-4fbf-bd2f-404a685f5472.text:
You're so clever; I've overheard passing adventurers
say that there's some witch near here who changes
ghostspeak amulets.

d2c539bf-e26c-426f-9031-760364dccf95.title: Alice
d2c539bf-e26c-426f-9031-760364dccf95.text:
I think she lives a bit west of that mad Professor
Fenksomething, past the Farming patch.

a0babdff-0e5e-405e-bfa5-23fc769af63c.title: <player>
a0babdff-0e5e-405e-bfa5-23fc769af63c.text:
I'll see if I can find her. Big nose and a monstrous hat,
I assume? I wonder where the beautiful young witches
hide...

63643d5b-762f-4094-a597-7d1e99eeee07.title: Alice
63643d5b-762f-4094-a597-7d1e99eeee07.text:
Mysterious indeed, but in this case she actually looks
pretty normal.

d49dfbee-c231-4e30-8d7b-5f936cbd4c1c.title: Alice
d49dfbee-c231-4e30-8d7b-5f936cbd4c1c.text:
Have you found a way for me to talk to my husband
yet?

37697a5c-df98-4f38-962e-11722f1fa178.title: <player>
37697a5c-df98-4f38-962e-11722f1fa178.text: I've not progressed at all, I'm afraid.

2d9a0b85-3c28-4f8b-9af9-907fdeeeae9d.title: <player>
2d9a0b85-3c28-4f8b-9af9-907fdeeeae9d.text:
I have obtained the amulet; I just haven't handed it
over yet. So, it's looking good!

ea9874ed-7fb8-4d7a-a6f6-0134a3187df8.title: Alice
ea9874ed-7fb8-4d7a-a6f6-0134a3187df8.text: Have you handed him an enhanced amulet?

1ce4005d-12e5-46c8-b225-5f658a3d0911.title: <player>
1ce4005d-12e5-46c8-b225-5f658a3d0911.text: I know how to make it; it will be done soon, I hope.
